title: 56a: Gayest Podcast Ever (Justin Martindale, Shawn Halpin)
itunes:title: Gayest Podcast Ever with Justin Martindale and Shawn Halpin - Part 1
description: Justin Martindale talked to us about his gay adventure in Dallas. I was there with him and Shawn Halpin to play the Addison Improv and Justin stopped by my hotel room and talked to Shawn and I about the gayest day I have ever heard of. And I live in West Hollywood, CA.
